name: Vintage pearl locket
description: Keep a piece of hidden treasure with you at all times with this nautical themed necklace featuring a brass shell locket, keeping safe a hidden pearl. This comes on a 48cm gold plated chain with added pearls.

name: Tea cup brooch
description:
Love tea? We do too! That’s why we designed these cute brooches for you… or the tea lover in your life.

Each badge is hand painted onto recycled wood by Lucy and then glazed to keep it waterproof (though we wouldn’t recommend wearing it in the shower!)

Size: 38mm/1.5 inches

name: Red heart embroidered purse
description:
Literally, a  lovely little purse to keep your cards, coins and any other bits and bobs safe. 

It's made from the offcuts of a vintage dress, so it’s very limited edition (only two purses left!), lined with a red cotton fabric and embroidered with a hand drawn heart in matching thread. 

Size: Approximately 3 x 4 inches

name: Panda brooch
description:
This pretty panda portrait makes everyone who sees him smile, so wear him on your lapel to cheer up everyone you meet. 

He is hand painted onto recycled wood by Lucy and then glazed to make this cute little brooch waterproof (though we don’t suggest having a bath with it!) 

Size: 38mm/1.5 inches

Due to the handmade nature of this item, please note that each brooch will look a little different.

name: Ampersand necklace
description:
One for typography lovers everywhere, this gold plated & "ampersand" charm is simple yet striking. It looks great over a collared shirt.

The charm comes on a 45cm gold plated curb chain.

name: Needlepoint necklace
description:
A tiny floral cameo that looks like a cross stitch picture and moving brass scissors - this necklace is a sewing lovers dream! 

Size: 18 inch/45cm gold plated chain

name: Flower power coin purse
description:
This sweet little floral purse is made from a vintage floral fabric and appliqued with a light green felt heart. 

Each purse measures 3 x 4 inches, making it the perfect size to keep your cards, coins and any little bits and bobs safe.

name: 'Hi' embroidered brooch
description:
Say 'hi' to everyone you meet with this sweet salutation embroidered on to vintage fabric and made into a brooch.

Size: 38mm/1.5 inches

name: 'Lovely' embroidered coin purse
description:
Tell everyone just how lovely you are with this sweet little purse.

It's is made from the offcuts of a vintage dress, so it’s very limited edition (only two purses left!) It's lined with a lilac fabric and embroidered with my own handwriting in purple thread.

Each purse measures 3 inches by 4 inches, making it the perfect size to keep your cards, coins and any little bits and bobs safe.

name: Crystal heart necklace
description:
Add a touch of class to any outfit with this simple necklace featuring a crystal heart charm and a tiny vintage brass bow on a 45cm gold plated chain.

Choose from regal purple or fancy leopard print!

name: Heart patch coin purse
description:
Wear your heart on your purse with this cute little zipped number mixing a sweet vintage floral fabric, polkadot lining and a heart-shaped corduroy patch.

It’s the perfect size for cards, rail tickets and some loose change.

name: Kitty brooch
description:
For cat lovers everywhere, here’s a cute kitty brooch to wear on your coat. This puss’s portrait has been hand painted by Lucy on to recycled wood before being glazed to protect it from the rain.

Size: 38mm/1.5 inches

name: 'Smile' embroidered brooch
description:
Remind everyone you meet to turn that frown upside down with this cheery polka dot brooch embroidered with the word SMILE!

Size: 38mm/1.5 inches

name: Lucky horseshoe coin purse
description:
Carry a little bit of luck around with you with this horseshoe patterned purse with a contrasting green bow and lining.

It measures approximately 3 by 4 inches so is the perfect size to keep your cards, coins and any other bits and bobs safe.

name: Vintage fabric button necklace
description:
These necklaces really are cute as a button and a pop of floral to any outfit.

Each button measures 20cm and is covered in a vintage fabric, making them very limited edition!

They are set in a pretty antique brass scalloped edge setting and come on a 24 inch/60cm antique brass chain.

name: Pencil doodle coin purse
description:
A cute pastel purse for anyone that loves to doodle. 

It may not be big enough to keep your pencils in, but it is the perfect size to keep your cards, coins and any little bits and bobs safe.

This purse is made from the offcuts of a vintage dress, so it’s very limited edition. It's lined with a light pink fabric and embroidered with a hand drawn design in turquoise thread. 

Size: Approximately 3 x 4 inches

name: Vintage floral zip purse
description:
A large zip purse, made with recycled and vintage floral fabrics, that’s large enough to keep your makeup or pens and pencils in, but small enough to carry around in your bag.  

There are three patterns to choose from with co-ordinating linings: Cream flowers/pink, Lilac flowers/purple, Turquoise flowers (Liberty fabric)/teal.

name: Crafty brooch
description:
For the sewing, knitting or drawing enthusiast in your life… or perhaps just for yourself.

This collection of brooches celebrates our creative loves. Each one is designed and hand painted onto recycled wood by Lucy before being glazed to keep them waterproof (though we don’t suggest going for a swim with one!) 

Size: 38mm/1.5 inches

name: Leather envelope necklace
description:
A tiny hand sewn leather envelope on a 24 inch antique brass chain. 

Use it to carry around whatever you want to keep close to your heart.

name: Mint scalloped zip purse
description:
A large zip purse made from a vintage stripey fabric, mint cotton lining and a felt scalloped applique.

It's large enough to keep your makeup or pens and pencils in, but small enough to carry around in your handbag.

name: Tea party necklace
description: We're all mad here! This charming Alice in Wonderland inspired necklace includes gold-plated tea pot, tea cup and top hat charms fixed on a 45cm gold chain.

name: Peter Pan collar necklace
description:
Dress up a plain tee with a pretty rounded collar necklace designed to sit just on your neckline.

This collar is made from a pretty floral vintage fabric, lined with cotton and hung on a gold-plated curb chain. 

The necklace measures 22 inches, but if you need a longer chain, just send a message before purchasing.

name: Vintage fabric bow necklace
description:
Spruce up a plain tee or wear with a collar for the classic shirt and bowtie look - with a twist!

Handmade from vintage fabrics, these sweet necklaces are truly unique. 

Each bow comes on a gold-plated trace chain measuring 45cm/18 inches, which means it should sit on your neckline, but send us a message before ordering if you need a longer chain.

name: Sewing kit necklace
description:
A tiny sewing machine, bobbin and thimble make up this cute little necklace. The perfect present for any sewing enthusiast! 

Choose from silver and gold plated.

Size: 18 inches/45cm long

name: Floral owl
description:
These owls are made from vintage and recycled fabrics, meaning that each one is truly unique. Their wings and faces are made of felt and carefully hand stitched by Fi.

Sizes vary, but each owl is up to 3.5 x 5 inches /9 x 13cm. They’re padded with a safe hi-loft polyester.  Although there are no small parts, supervision of children with this item is recommended.

name: Embroidered chevron necklace
description:
Wear a little piece of needlework round your neck with this hand embroidered chevron necklace in turquoise, pink and blue.

Each piece of embroidery is hung on a 45cm gold plated curb chain.

name: 'Hello' coin purse
description:
Say 'hello' to the cashier every time you get out this lovely little zip purse to pay. 

It's made from the offcuts of a vintage dress, so it's very limited edition, lined with a light blue fabric and embroidered with my own handwriting in a matching thread.

Each purse measures 3 by 4 inches, making it the perfect size to keep your cards, coins and any little bits and bobs safe.

name: Flower power clutch purse
description:
A clutch purse with real flower power! This envelope clutch is made from genuine 1970s Marks & Spencer fabric. 

It's lined to make it sturdy enough to carry around in your hand and is big enough to hold a phone, purse and a few extras. 

Alternatively, it could be used as a pencil case or make up bag.

name: Leather feather necklace
description: A beautiful feather design cut into contrasting recycled leather, punched with a brass eyelet and hung on a 21 inch antique bronze chain.

name: Mint floral zip purse
description:
A large zip purse, made with a vintage floral and appliqued with a felt heart. 

It's the perfect size to use as a makeup or pencil case.

name: Tiny creatures necklace
description:
This summery necklace is inspired by my own little garden, where I watch beautiful butterflies and other tiny winged creatures buzzing around the colourful flowers.

It features a bright siam orange pear jewel and two beautifully detailed insect charms; a brass hornet and a copper butterfly, all on an 18 inch/45cm gold-plated chain.

name: Embroidered bunting necklace
description: Three hand-stitched triangles in red, gold and teal hung on a 45cm gold plated curb chain to make this pretty embroidered bunting style necklace.

name: Rain drop necklace
description: A opalescent rain drop and a tiny brass umbrella charm on an 18 inch/45cm gold plated chain.

name: Paris Je T'aime necklace
description:
Aah Paris, the most romantic city in the world. Celebrate all things romantic with this sweet little necklace. 

It includes a "Je t'aime" pendant, tiny Eiffel Tower, heart and pearl on an 18 inch/45cm antique brass chain, topped off with a cream silk bow.

name: Rainy day necklace
description:
Rain, rain go away, come again another day.

We made this necklace in honour of the great British tradition that is never knowing when it's going to start chucking it down. So, it's always wise to carry an umbrella with you... even if it is just a teeny-weeny one around your neck! 

As well as a brass umbrella, this necklace features a blue raindrop givre jewel. All on an 18 inch/45cm gold-plated necklace.

name: Lady cameo necklace
description:
Bring a touch of class to any outfit with this pretty portrait necklace. 

It includes a tiny and beautifully detailed cameoin a gold-plated open back setting, accompanied by a pearl bead and petite brass fleur-de-lis charm, all on an 18 inch/45cm gold-plated chain.

name: Russian doll necklace
description: A sweet mini matryoshka with a tiny brass bow and pearl on an 18 inch/45 cm gold-plated chain.

name: Pearl on a plate necklace
description: This is a classic and unique necklace, featuring an antique brass engraved plate and a pearl bead on an 18 inch/45cm gold plated chain.

name: Postcard from Paris necklace
description:
This chic silver necklace includes a tiny flower, Eiffel Tower and working locket with the simple message "I love you".

Size: 18 inch/45cm silver plated chain

name: Silver swallow locket
description: A tiny silver plated working locket with a black jewel and matching silver swallow on an 18 inch/45 cm chain.

name: Apple a day necklace
description: A silver plated apple hangs from an antique brass branch on this lovely necklace. It comes on an 18 inch/45cm silver chain and would make a unique gift for a teacher.

name: Fairy Birthday Card
description:
Greetings Card A6 size (105/148mm)

Blank inside for your own message 

Printed on high quality card  

Individually packaged in a clear polybag with a white envelope

Greetings Card A6 size (105/148mm)

name: 'We Make A Lovely Pear!' Valentine's Card
description:
Greetings Card A6 size (105/148mm)

Blank inside for your own message 

Hand drawn on good quality card stock

Individually packaged in a clear polybag with a white envelope

Due to the hand drawn nature of this product the image may vary very slightly from the product picture.

description:
Greetings Card A6 size (105/148mm)

Blank inside for your own message 

Hand drawn on good quality card stock

Individually packaged in a clear polybag with a white envelope

name: Toadstool necklace
description: Add a splash of colour to any outfit with this cute necklace featuring a tiny glass toadstool charm on a long 56cm silver curb chain.

name: 'A is for Alice' necklace
description:
This sweet Alice in Wonderland necklace features a tiny illustration from the original Lewis Carroll book and is complemented with even smaller brass flamingo and letter 'A' charms. Perfect for any Wonderland lover, or someone called Alice! 

The illustration in a brass setting measures 18x33mm and comes on a 45cm curb chain.

name: 'Down the rabbithole' necklace
description: "I'm late, I'm late, for a very important date" so says the White Rabbit looking at his watch. This lovely little necklace features an illustration of this infamous character from the original Lewis Carroll book and is topped off with a pair of brass clock hands. The illustration comes in a brass setting measuring 18x33mm and comes on a 45cm gold plated curb chain.

name: Miniature teapot necklace
description: Any time is time for tea with a cute miniature dolls house teapot worn around your neck. Choose from three different colour pots, each on a 56cm gold plated trace chain.

name: 'Time for tea' necklace
description:
Show your appreciation for the great British tradition of a nice cuppa with a cute dolls house miniature tea cup worn around your neck. 

Choose from a blue floral design with a tiny a clock charm or a pink floral design with a mini tea pot. Both come on a 45cm gold plated chain.

name: 'Puppy love' dog charm necklace
description:
This is a necklace for all the dog lovers, featuring a tiny vintage dog portrait cabochon paired with a sweet gold plated terrier charm. 

The pendant measures 18x33mm and comes on a 45cm gold plated curb chain.

name: Penny farthing necklace
description:
A sweet little victoriana inspired necklace featuring a vintage-style penny farthing charm, a swooping swallow and a tiny heart, all topped off with a bright red flower. 

Available in silver or antique gold on a 41cm chain.

name: Vintage floral necklace
description: Wear a little work of art round your neck with this beautiful, unique rose picture painted onto porcelain. The pendant measures 38mm and comes on a 45cm gold plated trace chain.

name: Alice in Wonderland keyhole necklace
description:
This fun Alice in Wonderland necklace features an original John Tenniel illustration from Lewis Carroll's Alice in Wonderland, printed on to acrylic and laser cut into a cute keyhole shape. 

The charm measures 28mm wide x 46mm tall and comes on a 45cm silver plated trace chain.

name: Mad Hatter necklace
description:
This fun Mad Hatter necklace features an original John Tenniel illustration from Lewis Carroll's Alice in Wonderland, printed on to acrylic and laser cut. 

The charm measures 38mm wide x 41mm tall and comes on a 45cm silver plated trace chain.

name: White Rabbit necklace
description:
This White Rabbit necklace features an original John Tenniel illustration from Lewis Carroll's Alice in Wonderland, printed on to acrylic and laser cut. 

The charm measures 33mm wide x 43mm tall and comes on a 45cm silver plated trace chain.

name: Mr Moustache necklace
description:
A cute little laser cut acrylic moustache to wear around your neck. Each charm measures 40mm wide and comes on a 45cm trace chain.

Choose from a black moustache on a gold chain or white moustache on a silver chain.

name: 'Super' necklace
description: Don't be modest. Tell everyone how awesome you are with this 'super' brass word charm on a 45cm gold plated necklace.

name: Geek glasses necklace
description:
Show off your inner geek with a pair of black rimmed glasses to hang round your neck. 

The glasses pendant measure 70mm and comes on a choice of either a 45cm gold or silver plated trace chain.
